Yeah, I'm okay.

33
00:03:18,570 --> 00:03:20,769
Looks like we really fell down.

34
00:03:20,770 --> 00:03:23,469
Genta...

35
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:26,069
Hey, something's wrong with Genta!

36
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:28,170
Hey! Genta...

37
00:03:31,070 --> 00:03:33,170
Another grilled eel, please.

38
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:37,269
He hasn't slept since last night, right?

39
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:38,569
Genta!

40
00:03:38,570 --> 00:03:41,470
There's only 9 hours left until the time limit!

41
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:45,570
Where is this? Where are we?

42
00:03:47,570 --> 00:03:50,069
Remember what Mr. Clock said?

43
00:03:50,070 --> 00:03:55,269
Keep in mind, this Angel's Mansion is a huge labyrinth.

44
00:03:55,270 --> 00:03:57,669
A labyrinth. A labyrinth?

45
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:59,069
What do we do?

46
00:03:59,070 --> 00:04:00,770
There's nothing we can do but wait.

47
