No way...

48
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:08,770
So we can't get out of here?

49
00:04:12,070 --> 00:04:14,269
Mitsuhiko, it's all your fault.

50
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:16,769
What? It's not my fault!

51
00:04:16,770 --> 00:04:17,770
Yeah, it is.

52
00:04:17,771 --> 00:04:20,369
It's because you were trying to be cool in front Yuriko.

53
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:22,469
You're not that kind of guy. You shouldn't have acted like that.

54
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:24,169
Okay, but you were doing exactly the same thing,

55
00:04:24,170 --> 00:04:27,969
saying "I'm gonna beat Conan", weren't you?

56
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:30,069
Haibara and Ayumi, you girls were too!

57
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,569
I just...

58
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:33,069
I just wanted to...

59
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:34,569
You too, Conan!

60
00:04:34,570 --> 00:04:37,369
You ran into the Angel's tower, acting all self-righteous!

61
00:04:37,370 --> 00:04:39,969
Isn't that why this happened?

62
00:04:39,970 --> 00:04:42,469
You guys should've been waiting outside.

63
00:04:42,470 --> 00:04:43,969
What do you mean by that?

64
00:04:43,970 --> 00:04:47,869
You're saying Yuriko was kidnapped all because of us, not you!

65
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:49,970
-You wanna fight? -Why not?

66
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:55,970
It hurts...

67
